# Repo-root .gitignore for ~/ros_bag/
#
# Whitelist policy: ignore EVERYTHING at the top level by default, then
# explicitly allow only the source folder and the unzip helper script.
# Bag data (extracted folders like 20260419_050057/, *.zip, *.db3, ...)
# is therefore never accidentally committed.

# 1. Ignore everything in this directory.
/*

# 2. Re-allow the things we DO want under version control.
!/.gitignore
!/rosbag_analyzer/
!/unzip_bags.sh
